## Driver Infos

- **Device:** Compute Reference Design
- **SoC:** Snapdragon X1 Plus (`Purwa`)
- **Version:** `200.0.34.0`

## Driver Patches

### qcpmicgpio8450

- **Reason:** To properly Support PMIC GPIOs.
- **Patch:** Replaced `PeriphIrqInfo` Structure with the Structure from SC8280.
- **Creator:** [Robotix](https://github.com/Robotix22/)
